headline: Is Snowflake’s (SNOW) Anthropic Alliance Reframing Its Path From Data Warehouse to AI Orchestrator?
summary: In recent days, Snowflake and partners including Anthropic, Accenture, Collibra and Safe Software have expanded AI-focused collaborations and open data standards, while Snowflake reported higher quarterly sales and continued net losses alongside new product revenue guidance. Together, these moves deepen Snowflake’s role at the center of enterprise AI workflows, emphasizing governed data, interoperable semantics, and partner-led adoption across heavily regulated industries. We’ll now examine...
